snippet.title: [Flash game] Commando (Miniclip)
snippet.description:
Commando is Run 'n Gun shooting game by miniclip released in 2006

imitation of metal slug, but difference is there's health bar so you can assault way more aggressive

finally beat this game in 12 years after release i couldn't beat mission 4 somehow but i keep tried it there's safety spot in last boss so figure it out

also commando series is famous franchise in miniclip
